dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 10 feet up to 60 feet, 20 feet from 60 feet to 800 feet, 50 feet from 800 feet upwards, and spot heights. Set composed of 7 sheets. Accompanied by "central sheet" covering portions of sheets 3 and 4 with index to public buildings. Includes index to sheets and reliability diagram. Shows streets, roads, railways, public buildings and geographic features. "Published for the Jamaica Government by the British Government's Overseas Development Administration (Directorate of of Overseas Survey)."
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. Directorate of Overseas Surveys
dct_publisher_sm: Tolworth, Surrey : Directorate of Overseas Surveys, 1972.
